<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/62801ABJBVRSCKSBLJSPRBSBBBRLBKKGT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Holly Jolly Jill Barber Christmas";
  schema:description """
	If your idea of Christmas includes timeless songs, twinkling lights, and a little jazz, this one's for you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This November, Jill Barber returns to the Tidemark Theatre with A Holly Jolly Jill Barber Christmas, bringing her signature blend of jazz, folk, and pop to beloved Christmas classics and original holiday songs.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Joined by her jazz quartet, Jill creates the kind of concert that feels warm, relaxed, and timeless. It's an evening to pause, settle in, and enjoy the music that has a way of bringing people together year after year.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Known for her rich vocals and effortless stage presence, Jill has performed everywhere from Massey Hall and the National Arts Centre to audiences around the world. Whether she's singing a Christmas classic or one of her own beautifully crafted songs, she has a way of making every seat in the theatre feel like the best one in the house.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If your favourite part of the holidays is the music, A Holly Jolly Jill Barber Christmas is the perfect way to kick off the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $38.00 Members, $43.00 Non-Members <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
