<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/54001ABPSKBMMLLGTRJBVNRVDRDQRLGJK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Jim Witter - The Piano Men";
  schema:description """
	Spend an evening with one of Canada’s most beloved piano entertainers.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With a career spanning over 30 years, Jim Witter has built a reputation for unforgettable live performances that blend powerful vocals, masterful piano playing, and a genuine connection with his audience. Whether performing his own chart-topping originals or celebrating the music of icons like Billy Joel and Elton John, Jim creates a concert experience that is world-class and personal.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From intimate theatres to international stages across North America and the U.K., Jim Witter is known for shows that blend music, humour, and storytelling. His signature production, <span class=\"ItalicText\">The Piano Men</span>, has become a fan favourite, taking audiences through the hits of the 70s. A JUNO nominee with multiple Top 10 songs in Canada, Jim brings music and storytelling together in a way that feels personal and approachable.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Expect a feel-good night out filled with songs you know and moments you’ll remember.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $53 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
