  schema:description """
	SIXX PAXX DREAMS TOUR 2026/27<span><br/></span>WHEN FANTASIES COME TRUE<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Close your eyes and imagine your wildest night out—then watch it come to life. The SIXX PAXX DREAMS TOUR arrives in 2026/27, taking the internationally acclaimed sensation to the biggest stages they’ve ever played.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This all-new production turns up the heat with more seduction, more  passion, and more unforgettable moments—featuring electrifying<span><br/></span>choreography, live vocals, and a high-impact show that begins like a dream and stays with you long after the final bow.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Perfect for a girls’ night out, birthday celebration, or bachelorette party, SIXX PAXX delivers an interactive, high-energy experience<span><br/></span>where fantasy meets world-class performance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $99.00 VIP includes Meet & Greet, $69.00 Premium, $55.00 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(includes GST + applicable fees)</span>
""";
